本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:蘇美文研究生(外文):Su Mei-Wen論文名稱:電信業人力資源管理－以中華電信、台灣大哥大為例指導教授:林財丁學位類別:碩士校院名稱:東海大學系所名稱:管理碩士學程在職進修專班學門:商業及管理學門學類:其他商業及管理學類論文出版年:2003畢業學年度:91語文別:中文論文頁數:101中文關鍵詞:人力資源規劃、人力資源資訊系統、電信業、自由化外文關鍵詞:Human resource planning、Human resource information system、Telecommunication industry、Deregulation相關次數:

被引用:3點閱:1621評分:下載:0書目收藏:0



           電信產業屬於未來十大明星產業，在台灣經濟陷入一片不景氣當中，唯有電信產業一枝獨秀。而國內電信於2001年7月1日固網正式開放後，台灣電信自由化已趨完全，進入了電信的戰國時代，市場由賣方轉為買方，電信業者需提供更多樣化、資費更低的電信服務，以取得市場占有率，利潤空間也逐漸的被壓縮，更在WTO的催化下，走向國際化。而人力資源是電信業者決戰勝負的關鍵因素。基此，電信業者如何因應未來環境的變革、分析組織人力的需求，並規劃必要的措施，即「適時、適才、適量、適所」的人力資源規劃模式，以面對電信競爭市場，是本研究的動機。目的經由對人力資源規劃文獻、理論模式的探討，深入瞭解人力資源的涵意、特性、程序及運作方式，再配合電信業的趨勢及人力資源特色，建立一較理想的電信業人力資源規劃模式，進而對電信業者的人力資源規劃提出較具體的建議，以期能供電信業者從事人力規劃時之參考。           本研究採探索性的研究，透過次級資料的蒐集及訪談我國營業規模較大的二家電信業者為個案分析對象，研究結果建議：           1、 擁有歷史優久或組織龐大企業的領導者應有的覺醒與重點任務即是負責放一把火，讓大象般的僵化組織看到火焰、濃煙，忘記舊的約制而動起來。           2、 重「質」與「量」的人力資源盤點及預測。           3、 提早規劃接班計畫對由內部升任的企業更形重要。           4、 以職務調動刺激僵化組織。           5、 外包人力的約制與訓練。           6、 提早規劃電信經營管銷及國際人才。           7、 改變訓練部門以績效為目標的成果導向。           8、 人力資源規劃與人力資源資訊系統整合。

           The telecommunication industry belongs to the ten greatest stars industry of future. The Taiwanese telecommunication has deregulated completely when the fixed network opens on July 1 of 2001. The market turn to buyer from selling party, so the enterprises need to provide more variety and low fee of service to obtain the market rate. The profits also are compressed gradually. It trend internationalization under the WTO catalyst. And the human resource is the key factor of the competitive market for the telecommunication enterprise. How the operator respond the environment of future, analysis organization manpower of need, and program the measure of the necessity, then" in good time, fitting ability, just the right amount, suitable position" of the human resource planning mode, is the motive of this research.           The purpose is through the cultural documents and theories mode study to thorough understanding the meanings, characteristic, procedure and operation methods of the human resource. And match with the trend and human resource special features of the telecommunication industries; establish a more ideal telecommunication industry human resource planning mode. Then put the more concrete suggestion to the telecommunication enterprise when they implement human resource planning.           This paper adopts the exploratory research. Secondary data collection and case study base on the biggest two telecommunication companies. Finally, we have come to the suggestion as follows:           1、 The leader of the enterprise that history is excellent long and organization is huge must put a fire. Let the organization which look like an elephant and deadlock forget the old Conditioning and start to move.           2、 Both “quality" and" quantity" are important to verify and estimate the human resource.           3、 The enterprise whose promotion is from the inner, Program Replacement Plan is important.           4、 With the duty transfer to stimulate a deadlock organization.           5、 The manpower of outsourcing is in the control of contract and training.           6、 It is important to program the telecommunication manager, marketers and international human resource in advance.           7、 The changes the section the result that regards the performances as the target of trains.           8、 The human resource planning integrates with the human resource information system.

